        "body": { "en": "This is the right motor — mirror of the left. The cable connector faces right.", "zh": "这是右边那台电机——与左边镜像，线缆接头朝右。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:120mm; width:78mm;"
