      { "src": "motor_30_pulley_assembled_cam0_ghfe.svg" }
    ],
    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Two heights, on purpose", "zh": "故意分成两个高度" },
        "body": { "en": "The A and B belts run on two stacked planes. Set Motor A's pulley (left) to the lower plane and Motor B's (right) to the upper — slide each along the shaft, then lock its set screw.", "zh": "A、B 两条同步带分别走上下两层。电机 A 的同步轮（左）放下层，电机 B 的同步轮（右）放上层——各自沿电机轴滑到位，再拧紧紧定螺钉锁住。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:40mm; top:20mm; width:80mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Set screws", "zh": "紧定螺钉" },
        "body": { "en": "<p>Apply threadlocker to every set screw — no exceptions. Loose set screws are the most common problem users report; a drop now saves hours of troubleshooting later. Follow the directions on your threadlocker.</p>", "zh": "<p>每颗紧定螺钉都要涂螺纹胶，一颗都不能漏。紧定螺钉松动是用户反馈最多的问题；现在滴上一滴，能省下日后好几个小时的排查。涂法照螺纹胶的说明来。</p>" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:110mm; width:80mm;"
      }
    ],
    "bom": {
      "label": { "en": "Bill of materials", "zh": "物料清单" },
